00:38:51,050 --> 00:38:53,360
杰西卡  我觉得我们不需要不记名投票
Jessica, I don't think we're gonna be needing the ballots.

974
00:38:54,310 --> 00:38:56,050
我们每个人都知道自己的立场
I think everybody knows where they stand.

975
00:38:57,310 --> 00:38:59,220
所有支持杰西卡留下的人  举手
All in favor of Jessica staying.

976
00:39:08,640 --> 00:39:10,350
那我想这里所有人都很乐意
Then I guess everyone here is happy

977
00:39:10,350 --> 00:39:13,580
事情保持原状  除了一位
keeping things the way they are, except for one.

978
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,710
太好了你在这儿  我有话跟你说
I'm glad you're here. I need to tell you something.

979
00:39:31,430 --> 00:39:33,080
无论要说什么  我给你这个之后
Whatever it is, it might not matter

980
00:39:33,080 --> 00:39:34,490
就都不重要了
after I give you this.

981
00:39:34,860 --> 00:39:35,680
那是什么
What is it?

982
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:41,030
哈维  你不光给了我梦想
Harvey, you didn't just give me my dream.

983
00:39:43,680 --> 00:39:45,050
还给了我一个家
You gave me a family.

984
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:49,660
