and I can't have all of this hanging over their heads.

986
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:58,550
你要辞职
You're resigning.

987
00:40:00,660 --> 00:40:01,450
是的
I am.

988
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:07,730
你记得有次你问我为什么雇你
You know, you once asked me why I hired you,

989
00:40:09,220 --> 00:40:13,710
我跟你说  因为生活的高度在这里
and I told you it was because life is like this

990
00:40:14,730 --> 00:40:16,020
而我在这里
and I like this.

991
00:40:16,020 --> 00:40:17,350
哈维  拜托  你不可能劝我...
Harvey, please, you can't convince me--

992
00:40:17,350 --> 00:40:18,500
让我说完
Let me finish.

993
00:40:19,870 --> 00:40:21,430
能有这个高度
It was like this

994
00:40:22,350 --> 00:40:24,320
原因不在于我们担的风险
not because of the risk we're taking.

995
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,890
而是因为你是你
it's because of who you are.

996
00:40:30,120 --> 00:40:31,540
所以你不失望
So you're not disappointed?

997
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:32,560
你开玩笑吗
Are you kidding me?

998
00:40:32,770 --> 00:40:36,090
说了那么多  你不这么做
After that speech, if you hadn't done this,

999
00:40:36,090 --> 00:40:37,310
我也会踢你走
I'd be kicking you out.

1000
00:40:38,790 --> 00:40:39,880
而且再说一句
And for the record,

1001
00:40:39,880 --> 00:40:42,330
你不是这里唯一获得更多家人的人
You're not the only one who got more family out of this deal.

1002
00:41:04,890 --> 00:41:06,480
你真的好美
You really are so beautiful.

1003
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:09,220
荧光灯底下没人美的
No one's beautiful in fluorescent light.

1004
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:10,170
你就美
You are.

1005
00:41:10,170 --> 00:41:13,840
你的神秘冒险怎么样了
So how did your mysterious adventure go?

1006
00:41:14,270 --> 00:41:15,570
得到你想要的东西了吗
Did you get what you needed?

1007
00:41:16,740 --> 00:41:17,540
得到了
I did.

1008
00:41:20,810 --> 00:41:21,710
这是什么
What's this?

1009
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:23,050
提前的结婚礼物
Early wedding present.

1010
00:41:32,260 --> 00:41:32,790
迈克  这是...
Mike, this is--

1011
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,700
我辞职信的副本
A copy of my letter of resignation.

1012
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:36,340
如果这跟克莱尔
If this is about the thing with Claire

1013
00:41:36,340 --> 00:41:37,580
或者我跟我妈妈的争吵有关...
or the fight that I got into with my mom--

1014
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:38,610
没关系
It's not.

1015
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:41,040
这只关于我们要好好开始我们的生活
This is about us starting our life right,

1016
00:41:42,650 --> 00:41:43,680
干干净净地开始
with a clean slate.

1017
00:41:43,680 --> 00:41:45,480
你不必为我这么做
You don't have to do this for me.

1018
00:41:45,490 --> 00:41:46,390
我不是为你
I'm not.

1019
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:48,840
是为了我们
I'm doing it for us.

1020
00:41:49,050 --> 00:41:49,990
因为只要你支持我...
Because as long as you're with me--

1021
00:41:49,990 --> 00:41:51,010
我支持你
I'm with you.

1022
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:54,380
那就让我跟我的办公室说再见吧
Well then, let me go say good-bye to my office,

1023
00:41:55,380 --> 00:41:56,300
然后我们回家
and let's go home.

1024
00:42:09,180 --> 00:42:11,020
{\an8}奥登・斯佩克特

1025
00:42:16,070 --> 00:42:18,540
