1037
00:42:44,580 --> 00:42:46,980
该有人为你付出点东西了
It's time someone gave up something for you.

1038
00:42:46,980 --> 00:42:49,920
我不想让你做那个付出的人呢
What if I don't want you to be the one to do that?

1039
00:42:49,920 --> 00:42:51,900
那就原谅我  因为我要做
Then forgive me, because I am.

1040
00:42:53,530 --> 00:42:55,920
好消息是迈克・罗斯要离开
Good news is Mike Ross is leaving.

1041
00:42:56,960 --> 00:42:58,880
我从没想过我会这么说
I never thought I'd say this,

1042
00:42:59,890 --> 00:43:01,200
但现在
but this moment,

1043
